# ============================================================
# ENTROPY
# ============================================================

Typical Values

| Entropy | Meaning |
|---------|----------|
| 0.0 - 5.5 | Normal |
| 5.5 - 7.0 | Compressed |
| 7.0 - 8.0 | Packed / Encrypted |

Example

```
Entropy : 7.94
```

High Entropy Usually Means

✔ Packed

✔ Encrypted

✔ Compressed

